title: What's Your ONE Thing?
itunes:title: What's Your ONE Thing?
description:
Episode 639 - The One Thing is on of my top 3 favorite books. I read it at the perfect time and it made me shift my life and business dramatically which turned into what I do now. This is my in depth interview with the author Jay Papasan. He gives so much value in this episode, and I can't wait for you to listen to it! Follow me on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
